Package: altfuelr
Title: Provides an interface to the NREL Alternate Fuels Locator API
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Kitt",
           family = "Burch",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "christopher.m.burch@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6934-3325"))
Description: This package provides a number of functions to access the National Energy Research Laboratory (NREL) Alternate Fuel Locator API. The AFL shows the location of alternate fuel stations in the contiguous United States and can be filtered by fuel type, region, zip code, or address.
